    "[point-generating, pure html/d3](http://bl.ocks.org/WilliamQLiu/76ae20060e19bf42d774)\n",
    "\n",
    "[dragging points, d3/jupyter](https://mpld3.github.io/examples/drag_points.html)\n",
    "\n",
    "NOTES\n",
